text: Thatta is a city in Sindh, Pakistan. Thatta may also refer to: *Thatta District, an administrative unit of Sindh, Pakistan *Thatta, Attock, a town in Punjab, Pakistan *Thatta Jhamb, a village in Punjab, Pakistan *Thatta, Sultanpur Lodhi, a village in Punjab, India ==See also== * * *Thattamala, a neighbourhood in Kollam, India
title: Thatta (disambiguation)
